    {
      "kind": "parameters",
      "languages": [
        "occ"
      ],
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "timerID",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The ID of the timer you want to arm. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "expirationTime",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A pointer to a value that specifies when you want the timer to expire. Note that if you arm the timer with a time that has already passed, the timer expires immediately. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "options",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Any optional actions. See "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1585611-timer_option_masks"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " for a list of possible values. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A result code. See "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/carbon_core/multiprocessing_services#1663965"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If the timer has already expired, the reset does not take place and the function returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "kMPInsufficientResourcesErr"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The expiration time is an absolute time, which you can generate by calling the Driver Services Library function "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "UpTime"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". When the timer expires, a notification is sent to the notification mechanism specified in the last  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1585726-mpsettimernotify"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "  call. If the specified notification ID has become invalid, no action is taken when the timer expires. The timer itself is deleted when it expires unless you specified the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "kMPPreserveTimerID"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " option in the options parameter."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Also see the function  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1585745-mpcanceltimer"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
